Class LiteralExpr

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class LiteralExpr
extends Expr

Represents a Literal.

The tag of a LiteralExpr should be one of the *LIT (eg INTLIT) constants defined in TagConstants. The value fields is a Character/String/Long/Double/Boolean/null, as appropriate.
